ard, I cant heal, so I generally root the MOB then tell them to back up to get healing from someone else (hopefully)or run, and if they run Ill finish the MOB. I have been playing foe about 6 months now and have been acused of KS only once and this was due to a major lag problem on the day.<P>BTW, My guild will go out of its way to help anyone in need. If you see any of us on, dont hesitate to call on us if you get over your head.<P>Arryen, LvL 14 Wizard<BR>The Rusty Blade <BR>Veeshan</FONT></TD></TR></TABLE></td></tr></table> 
